name: Sky Way
description:
The goal is to reach the black square.

Try to get there in time!

Control with arrows:

Up - Jump

Left - Go left

Right - Go right

Music: Little Star by Manuele Atzeni

https://freemusicarchive.org/music/Manuele_Atzeni/The_Miyazaki_Tour_EP/Little_St...

The game is based on a HTML platformer by Martynas Linkevicius:

https://codepen.io/iiSeptum/pen/RwaXvw

Level design and additional coding: Magnus Lindh
